oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Airplane Filling Station [ca. 1931] by Robin Thompson

oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Airplane Filling Station [ca. 1931] taken by Robin Thompson. The Airplane Filling Station was built in 1929 by Henry and Elmer Nickle, located on Clinton Highway (near Callahan Road), Knox County, TN. Texaco gasoline.
